Adding JRebel support to console development; three Maven profiles (besides default one) are now available:
 1. dev - for console development WITHOUT JRebel
 2. jrebel - for console development WITH JRebel (requires env variable REBEL_HOME and "mvn compile" when needing refresh)
 3. selenium - for Selenium tests
